Package: shinymcp
Title: Convert Shiny Apps to MCP Apps
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("James", "Wade", , "github@jameshwade.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Converts existing Shiny applications into MCP (Model Context
    Protocol) Apps that render inside AI chat interfaces. Provides a
    parse-analyze-generate pipeline for automatic conversion, MCP-compatible
    UI components, a JavaScript bridge for the MCP Apps postMessage protocol,
    and a runtime framework for serving MCP Apps with tools and ui:// resources.
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/JamesHWade/shinymcp, https://jameshwade.github.io/shinymcp/
BugReports: https://github.com/JamesHWade/shinymcp/issues
